description:
This outfit set includes costumes with 4 color variations for Yuji Itadori, Megumi Fushiguro, and Kugisaki Nobara that can be used during battles.

Includes:
• Yuji Itadori Costume: Rock Glasses
• Megumi Fushiguro Costume: Shikigami Accessory
• Nobara Kugisaki Costume: Squeaky Toy Hammer

*Please note that this product is included in bundles. Take care to avoid duplicate purchases.
name: Jujutsu Kaisen Cursed Clash - Jujutsu High First-Years Outfit Set
